Using mysql to set the database up how I currently have it set up:


~~Log user into MySQL~~
mpotter2782@Potato:~$ mysql -u root -p
Enter password: 


Welcome to the MySQL monitor.  Commands end with ; or \g.
Your MySQL connection id is 3
Server version: 5.7.12-0ubuntu1 (Ubuntu)

